                        <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Iohannes/Favaro">Iohannes
                            Favaro</name></persName> et <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Andreas"
                            >Andrea</name></persName> in tertiam partem de duobus iugera et
                        <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Gregorius">Gregorius</name></persName> et
                        <persName key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Ildebrandus">Ildebrando</name></persName> in
                        duabus partibus; scilicet in vos et in vestris heredibus usque in perpetuum.
                        Que autem iam dicta iugera sunt in <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/1566"><geogName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#estates/1126">Celula</geogName></placeName>, quorum vocabula
                        sunt curte de <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/1131"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes" ref="#places/1577">Paulecla</placeName></geogName> et
                        curte de <placeName key="#Curtes" ref="#places/2480"><geogName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#estates/1127">Radigosa</geogName></placeName>, et in curte
                            <geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/1130"><placeName key="#Curtes"
                                ref="#places/1575">Gisso</placeName></geogName> et in aliis locis,
                        ubicumque nunc date sunt vel inantea date erunt tantummodo ad habendum,
                        tenendum, fruendum, fatiendum, quicquid vobis utile erit, eo videlicet modo,
                        ut <rs key="#Castle">roccam</rs> de <placeName key="#Castle"
                            ref="#places/1576"><geogName key="#Castle" ref="#estates/1132"
                                >Gissadello</geogName></placeName>, pro qua hec omnia do vobis, ab
                        hac ora inantea incastellare, guitare et laborare et claudere debetis, sicut
                        decet et conveniens erit, ita ut omni anno de mense martio <rs
                            key="#Rent_in_money">denariorum Veneticorum persolvere debeatis per
                            unumquemque iugerum</rs> ad <orgName key="#Rent_in_money"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/47"><placeName ref="#places/15">ecclesiam sancti
                                Silvestri</placeName></orgName> usque in perpetuum. Si vero predicta
                        rocca permanserit et si domina Matilda in aliquo modo eam reliquerit vel
                        vastaverit sine ulla occasione, que fieri potest, predictam cartulam
                        deinceps permaneat usque in perpetuum. Et promitto ego domina predicta
                        Matilda tam pro me quam pro meos successores vobis supradictis petitoris vel
                        vestris heredibus usque in perpetuo defensare auctorizare. Si qua vero pars,
                        qui contra hanc paginam emphyteotecaria ire temptaverint et non
                        observaverint omnia, quod superius legitur, tunc componat illa pars, qui hoc
                        non observaverint, ad partem fidem servantem pene nomine solidi centum
                        denariorum Lucensium, et post penam solutam cartulam precariam maneat in sua
                        firmitate. Actum in loco <placeName ref="#places/269">sancti
                            Cesarii</placeName>. Supra legitur: Matilda dei gratia, si quid est,
                        subscripsi. Ego <persName key="#Witness #Archpriests"><name ref="Danihel"
                                >Daniel</name></persName>
                        <placeName key="#Archpriests #Witness" ref="#places/446"
                            >Montebelliensis</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Archpriests">archipresbiter</rs>
                        <rs key="#Witness">interfui</rs>. <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Hubaldus">Ubaldo</name></persName> de <placeName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#places/">Scoveto</placeName> et + <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Hughicio">Ugizone</name></persName> filius <persName><name
                                ref="Rainerius">Ragineri</name></persName>. <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Gandulfus">Gandulfo</name></persName> da <placeName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#places/">Broilo</placeName> namque + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rodulfus">Rodulfo</name></persName> de
                            <placeName key="#Witness" ref="#places/">Monte Claro</placeName> rogati
                        sunt. Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Conone"
                            >Conon</name></persName> subscripsi et fieri rogavi. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Priors" ref="#people/3502">Iohannes</persName> dictus <rs
                            key="#Priors">prior</rs> vidi et scripsi. In dei nomine, ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Tabellio"><name ref="Leo">Leo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> hanc cartulam precariam, sicut superius
                        legitur, <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et complevi. Dominus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Nicolaus">Nicholaus</name></persName> et
                        dominus <persName key="#Witness #Judge"><name ref="Zaccarus"
                            >Zaccarus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudices</rs> de comuni <placeName key="#Witness #Judge"
                            ref="#places/7"><orgName key="#Witness #Judge"
                                ref="#juridical_persons/1119">Bononie</orgName></placeName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Causidicus"><name ref="Pegoloctus"
                                >Pegoloctus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Causidicus">causidicus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ardicionus">Ardicono</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Rainerius">Rainerius</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petro</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Aldizo">Aldizone</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Zuccherus">Zuccherus</name></persName> ad hanc
                        cartam antiquam et novam audiendam interfuere et huius rei causa testes
                        vocati sunt. Ego <persName key="#Copyist #Notary"><name ref="Hugo"
                                >Ugo</name></persName> dei gratia comunis Bononie <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> hoc presens instrumentum, ut vidi in antiquo, subscripsi
